snippet.title: 【Lyric MV】Florence "Flag" (Full Ver.) 【MementoMori】
snippet.description:
This is a Lament (original character theme song) from MementoMori, a new RPG that released on 10.18.2022.

==================================
A knight who was brainwashed by the enemy
into hurting the friend dearest to her.
“Florence”
==================================
